entries.journal_entry_description: I'm actually working for Captain Dustrunner. He thinks I'm his long lost undercover agent. I'll have to do whatever I can to keep him happy until I get Borvo's information settled.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: This Aldalad is planning to testify against Borvo. If I want Borvo to help me I'd better take this guy out. At least he's not innocent, just greedy.
entries.task01_message_box_text: This is where Aldalad is supposed to meet you. Find him and take him out!
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: I have to take care of Aldalad to make sure he doesn't testify against Borvo before I get what I want.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: I need to make up some story for Captain Dustrunner. I'll think of something on the way back to see him.
